    "Management": {
      "text": "Doxycycline\n100 mg BID for 5-7 days\n[4]\nIndicated also in children at 2.2mg/kg BID\nChloramphenicol\n(CAM) 50-100 mg/kg/day div Q6hr (Max dose = 4g/day)\nPreferred agent in pregnancy. May cause\naplastic anemia\nand\nGrey baby syndrome\n, more common in near term or 3rd trimester\n[1]\nConsideration should be made for doxycycline over CAM in the 3rd trimester",
